Subject: drm/amdgpu: make sure BOs are locked in amdgpu_vm_get_memory
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: e2ad8e2df432498b1cee2af04df605723f4d75e6
Patch-mainline: v6.5-rc1
References: jsc#PED-9898 jsc#PED-10191 jsc#PED-10197 jsc#PED-10226 jsc#PED-10237 jsc#PED-10340 jsc#PED-10852 jsc#PED-11022 bsc#1012628 bsc#1212848

We need to grab the lock of the BO or otherwise can run into a crash
when we try to inspect the current location.

